data.description: A cozy 3 bedroom, 1 bath house with many updates! Open concept kitchen/living room. First floor bathroom/laundry and first floor bedroom make this a 1 level living home! 2 large bedrooms upstairs and a large closet that could be made into a 1/2 bath! Off of the living room is the door for the back deck. Overlooking the large back yard and a mountain view! New retaining wall and parking .Newer roof and some new windows! 2 new mini split systems for additional heating and cooling, one on each floor! 2 large sheds included, one is set up as a play house with bunks for sleepouts! Come tour this well maintained home! **SELLER OFFERING A $10,000 CREDIT TO BUYER - Ask your agent for details!
